    <p>In a rare move, the Na­tional Wages Coun­cil (NWC)will re­view its wage guide­lines for a se­cond time this year as the Covid-19 pan­demic takes a toll on the labour mar­ket. More de­tails will be pro­vided later this month, The Straits Times un­der­stands.</p>


